name: VT Enterprise

overview:
VT Enterprise’s business is to enhance competitive advantage of clients in financial industry and beyond by intelligent use of computer technology.

The company has been serving Wall Street’s premier institutions since 2001 providing access to expert programmers and the highly specialized custom software solutions.

Company’s product offerings include:

  • /db (SlashDB), a software which automatically makes RESTful web services out or relational databases, and
  • Assetcloud - customized implementation of /db for data management and distribution in the securities industry (reference, market data, transactions, compliance, risk etc.)

Outside of finance, VT Enterprise’s /db has attracted developers of mobile enterprise applications, who leverage its automated API to access corporate databases for reading and writing in standard data formats such as JSON, XML and comma-separated values.
